sequenceDiagram
    actor P as Dueno PYME
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant IA as Motor IA
    participant DB as MySQL

    P->>FE: Completa wizard de negocio
    FE->>API: POST /api/businesses
    API->>DB: Guarda negocio
    FE->>API: POST /api/crowdfunding/requests
    API->>IA: Evalua riesgo y viabilidad
    IA-->>API: Dictamen + score
    API->>DB: Guarda solicitud
    API-->>FE: Solicitud creada
    P->>FE: Consulta estado/progreso
    FE->>API: GET /api/crowdfunding/requests/me
    API->>DB: Lee solicitudes propias
    API-->>FE: Lista de solicitudes
